00:10:32.222 --> 00:10:33.650
This is what the bilateral
enucleate looks like

00:10:33.650 --> 00:10:35.700
on this novel task, look at this.

00:10:35.700 --> 00:10:36.533
Bam.

00:10:36.533 --> 00:10:37.366
