00:10:41.128 --> 00:10:43.287
We propose that because the
whiskers are so important,

00:10:43.287 --> 00:10:45.740
you have this huge representation
of the whiskers now.

00:10:45.740 --> 00:10:47.345
We trimmed the whiskers.

00:10:47.345 --> 00:10:49.200
