They grew back, they grew back, okay?

00:10:51.070 --> 00:10:52.490
But check this out, this is so cool.

00:10:52.490 --> 00:10:55.470
Look, this is the same animal
with his whiskers trimmed,

00:10:55.470 --> 00:10:57.429
and here's what happens.

00:10:57.429 --> 00:10:59.060
